	<!-- Application market html -->
	<div class="section-column application white">
		<div class="section-screen">
			<div class="choice-flex">
				<div class="choice-flex-item" style="display: block;">
					<div class="text right">
						<div class="title">应用市场</div>
						<p class="describe">多方位进行商品管理, 监测商品购买数据, 提供多种工具优化店铺访问情况。</p>
						<!-- <button class="button marginTop consultNow">立即咨询</button> -->
					</div>
					<div class="image left"><img src="./assets/image/application.png" /></div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="application-grid">
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app01.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">复制店铺</div>
						<p class="describe">复制您的商品、评论、页面、物流设置及更多，更快的让您复制店铺，提高建站效率。

						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app02.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">快捷加购</div>
						<p class="describe">在详情页中添加快捷加购按钮, 方便买家在下滑浏览的过程中加入该商品到购物车, 最终提高转化。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app03.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">组合商品</div>
						<p class="describe">当需要提高客单价或者为其他商品进行引流时, 可以在详情页中添加组合商品。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app04.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">商品评论</div>
						<p class="describe">可以为商品添加评论, 为买家提供购买后的反馈, 以提高商品的加购率。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app05.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">促销倒计时</div>
						<p class="describe">可以为详情页和结账页添加倒计时功能, 给买家营造一种紧迫感和稀缺感, 以降低加购和结账的放弃率。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app06.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">运费险</div>
						<p class="describe">帮助卖家收取额外费用, 同时可以增加买家的信任, 此功能在各大平台都有很好的表现。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app07.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">推荐商品</div>
						<p class="describe">随机推荐建议的商品, 使其展示在其他商品的详情页中, 以提高客单价和转化。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="application-grid-item">
					<div class="image"><img src="./assets/image/app08.png" /></div>
					<div class="text">
						<div class="subtitle">最近购买记录</div>
						<p class="describe">商品详情页每隔几秒展示店铺的历史顾客购买记录, 营造网站热卖的气氛, 促使顾客购买。</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
